  chapterTitle: Dessert Rescue
  displayTitle: Sap Happens
  theme: 0
  openingStory: Amber sap has pooled across mossy branches. It smells like dessert,
    looks suspiciously inviting, and grabs with both hands.
  successStory: Two heroic rip-frees later, Gassy Gorilla is flying again, wearing
    a glossy amber souvenir.
  lessonText: Land on the amber sap snare. Once it grabs you, tap once to rip free
    without spending fuel.
  failureHintText: Follow the descending food arc, land in the amber sap, then tap
    once after it grabs you.
